HEADWORD: Examinant
<hw>Ex*am"i*nant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>examinans</ets>, <ets>-antis</ets>, examining.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
